{"tid":236083,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【浪漫滿車】深圳地鐵開表白專列 單身車廂「甜蜜蜜」","createTime":"2017-05-09T12:55:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-09T13:45:55.000Z","uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7b0b9695b179159b36293d8b4dfa0fae69a3f510","tid":236083,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T12:55:23.000Z","msg":"近日，深圳開了地鐵表白專列，將在1號線運行1個月，昨日開始行車，每天巡回行駛，專設單身專用車廂。在車廂內，有上千條表白訊息，內容有對喜歡的人的表白，有對父母的表白，對同學的表白，其中內容有：「同學，有沒有覺得對面那位很像你下任女朋友。」「我喜歡了你13年啊，你竟然都沒有發現，你說你是有多笨」<br />\n<br />\n另有對陌生人的表白，「每天上班都會重複同一條路，每次8點到8點半的時間裡，我總會在某個時間點和你相遇，很多次的遇見突然想下一次我們遇見了就交朋友吧，可是當看到你的時候，勇氣就沒有以前那麼強烈了，每天你都會從深大C口出口走來，在紅綠燈口相遇，你背着包，有時候會穿着格子襯衫，很安靜，我知道你就在金證大廈裡面上班，因為每天我都會路過。」<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170509/56670383\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170509%2F56670383&d=3UqZ%2FPYEUq8PtOmaimGdDZ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=b63051c3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170509%2F56670383&h=a5aa669c\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170509/56670383</a>"},{"pid":"282609cf48c416f67513ec8b2874ba6db7849b87","tid":236083,"uid":1567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T13:10:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Berhati-hati di ruang platform!!!!!</span>"},{"pid":"45d733e7baac74871be448623f2a9481ed87ad58","tid":236083,"uid":1567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T13:13:36.000Z","msg":"男︰aku cinta kamu...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n女︰BALIK KAMPUNG LAH!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d526666965bff0ce7530a139c52bc515f045ccbf","tid":236083,"uid":2126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T13:43:17.000Z","msg":"遲下就會變痴漢專用/全車毒撚"},{"pid":"2329849f8481df3aabe4673e3b211b00926985d1","ti